description: Describes the what-if analysis created using the  CreateWhatIfAnalysis operation. In addition to listing the properties provided in the CreateWhatIfAnalysis request, this operation lists the following properties:

parameters.name: WhatIfAnalysisArn
parameters.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the what-if analysis that you are interested in.

nested_items.name: WhatIfAnalysisName
nested_items.description: The name of the what-if analysis.

nested_items.name: WhatIfAnalysisArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the what-if analysis.

nested_items.name: ForecastArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the what-if forecast.

nested_items.name: EstimatedTimeRemainingInMinutes
nested_items.description: The approximate time remaining to complete the what-if analysis, in minutes.

nested_items.name: Status
nested_items.description: The status of the what-if analysis. States include:

nested_items.name: Message
nested_items.description: If an error occurred, an informational message about the error.

nested_items.name: CreationTime
nested_items.description: When the what-if analysis was created.

nested_items.name: LastModificationTime
nested_items.description: The last time the resource was modified. The timestamp depends on the status of the job:
ACTIVE or CREATE_FAILED - When the job finished or failed.

nested_items.name: TimeSeriesSelector
nested_items.description: Defines the set of time series that are used to create the forecasts in a TimeSeriesIdentifiers object.
